 "cells": [
  {"cell_type": "markdown", "metadata": {"id": "hdr"}, "source": [
    "# FPUS23 — YOLO SOTA All‑in‑One\n",
    "\n",
    "Pipeline:\n",
    "1) Despeckle + Balanced train set\n",
    "2) Train 2‑stage (768 → 896) with medical‑safe augs\n",
    "3) TTA validation + scale‑WBF fusion (768 + 896)\n",
    "4) Optional SAHI slice inference on val\n",
    "5) Optional pseudo‑label unlabeled images → short fine‑tune\n",
    "\n",
    "All steps save per‑epoch to Drive and auto‑resume.\n"
  ]},
  {"cell_type": "code", "metadata": {"id": "bootstrap"}, "execution_count": null, "outputs": [], "source": [
    "%pip -q install -U ultralytics opencv-python-headless ensemble-boxes sahi pyyaml\n",
    "from google.colab import drive\n",
